'''Shyaka Kagamé''' (yavutse 1983), ni umunya[[Rwanda]] uba muri [[Ubusuwisi|Swiss]] . Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ''Bounty'' ishimwa cyane.  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1983 i Geneve mu [[Busuwisi]] ku babyeyi b'u [[Rwanda]]. 

== Umwuga ==
Mbere yo kwinjira muri sinema, yize siyanse ya politiki. Mu 2009, Kagamé yatangiye umwuga we wa filime nk'umuyobozi wungirije hamwe n’umukinnyi wa firime wa Geneve Frédéric Baillif.  Muri Kamena 2017, Kagamé yerekanye bwa mbere ''Bounty'' .  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yerekanwa mu birori byinshi bya firime. Inyandiko irihariye kubera nta majwi arenga, kubazwa cyangwa isura ya kamera. Filime ivuga kubibazo bijyanye numwirondoro wabirabura  babasuwisi. 

